  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6740a12804732c9d38e80ce5",
      "text": "【兵庫県議会】令和6年 文書問題調査特別委員会（百条委員会）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288809
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc0b",
      "text": "from [【安野貴博vs高橋弘樹】なぜ東京都のアドバイザーに？【ReHacQ緊急生配信】]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288809
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1a1aff09e000050dc16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288930,
      "updated": 1732288930
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc0c",
      "text": "【兵庫県議会】令和6年8月30日 文書問題調査特別委員会（百条委員会）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288930
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc0e",
      "text": "[https://www.youtube.com/live/XfbmhrWWyEs?t=183s]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288809
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a19eaff09e000050dc15",
      "text": "[claude.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288926,
      "updated": 1732289004
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc18",
      "text": "兵庫県議会の文書問題調査特別委員会での斎藤元彦知事への証人尋問の主なポイントをまとめます：",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc1a",
      "text": "1. パワハラ関連の主な事案:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc1b",
      "text": "- 県立美術館での車止め問題：職員への強い口調での注意",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc1c",
      "text": "- 付箋投げ事件：片山副知事との会議中に付箋を投げる行為",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc1d",
      "text": "- 机叩き事件：就任直後に土木局長らへの威圧的行為",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc1e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc1f",
      "text": "2. 職員とのコミュニケーション問題:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc20",
      "text": "- 深夜・休日のチャットでの業務指示",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc21",
      "text": "- 知事協議の困難さ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc22",
      "text": "- 職員アンケートで約4割がパワハラを見聞き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc24",
      "text": "3. 知事の認識と対応:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc25",
      "text": "- 多くの場面で「当時の認識では適切だった」と主張",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc26",
      "text": "- パワハラとの明確な認識は示さず",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc27",
      "text": "- 一部行為については「不適切だった」と反省",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc28",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc29",
      "text": "4. 組織運営上の問題:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc2a",
      "text": "- 決裁規定違反の可能性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc2b",
      "text": "- 元県民局長への処分手続きの不適切さ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc2c",
      "text": "- 秘書室や職員への過度な要求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc2e",
      "text": "5. 今後の対応:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc2f",
      "text": "- 職員とのコミュニケーション改善を約束",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc30",
      "text": "- 不適切な行為があった職員への謝罪の意向を表明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1ecaff09e000050dc31",
      "text": "- 自身の言動に対する反省の必要性を認識",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289005,
      "updated": 1732289005
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a1f0aff09e000050dc32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289009,
      "updated": 1732289009
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc0f",
      "text": "【兵庫県議会】令和6年10月25日　文書問題調査特別委員会（百条委員会）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288926
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc10",
      "text": "[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CfFT8lotlYM]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288809
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc12",
      "text": "[claude.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732289101
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc33",
      "text": "文書は兵庫県議会の特別委員会での証人尋問の記録です。主な内容:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc35",
      "text": "1. 証人尋問の対象者:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc36",
      "text": "- 井本元総務部長",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc37",
      "text": "- 片山元副知事 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc38",
      "text": "- 小橋元県民センター長",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc3a",
      "text": "2. 主な尋問内容:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc3b",
      "text": "- 告発文書への対応と調査過程",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc3c",
      "text": "- パレードの資金調達に関する問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc3d",
      "text": "- 選挙運動への関与疑惑",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc3e",
      "text": "- 公益通報制度の運用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc3f",
      "text": "- 人事に関する問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc41",
      "text": "3. 重要な証言:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc42",
      "text": "- 告発文書を「不正な目的」と判断して調査を進めた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc43",
      "text": "- パレード資金調達で信用金庫等に働きかけを行った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc44",
      "text": "- 職員の個人情報を含む資料の取り扱いに問題があった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc45",
      "text": "- 第三者委員会設置の提案が知事に受け入れられなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc46",
      "text": "- 処分を急いだことへの反省の声",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc48",
      "text": "4. 特徴的な点:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc49",
      "text": "- 証人間で証言内容に食い違いが見られる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc4a",
      "text": "- 人事調査の適切性について議論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc4b",
      "text": "- 公益通報制度の運用に疑問の声",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a24daff09e000050dc4c",
      "text": "- 職員からの選挙関連の証言多数",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732289102,
      "updated": 1732289102
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288809
    },
    {
      "id": "6740a128aff09e000050dc14",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1732288809,
      "updated": 1732288809
    }
  ]
}